snippet.title: Final Fantasy II (Long) (WonderSwan Color) Japanese Commercial
snippet.description:
Incase you collapse in the middle of no where, it's good to have a portable console handy. Translation for the Japanese packaging of Final Fantasy II: https://chrisaaronblog.blogspot.com/2024/08/final-fantasy-ii-wonder-swan-color.html

My transcription of the audio:
このドラマ。。。忘れない
